Robia LaMorte https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robia_LaMorte 0 Robia Brett LaMorte, sometimes credited as Robia La Morte, is an American former actress and former dancer. She is best known as a dancer and spokesperson for the musician Prince, and for starring as Jenny Calendar in the television series Buffy the Vampire Slayer.
